<div id="content">
    <h2>Welcome!</h2>
    <p>
        Welcome to my personal home page. This site is currently under
        development, so please check back often for updates. Or don't. I'm
        grasping for straws here.
    </p>
    <p>
        I update this site frequently. Force reload (<code>Ctrl+Shift+R</code>
        or <code>Fn+F5</code> usually) every so often to get the latest
        version.
    </p>

    <p>
        <sup>Accessing from an older or more compact browser? Click
        <a href="/Lite/Simple">here</a>.</sup>
    </p>

    <p>
        If you got here from a webring, scroll down to get to your next
        stop. Feel free to peek at the
        <a href="/CalculatorMuseum">museum</a> or sign the
        <a href="/Guestbook">guestbook</a> on your way out!
    </p>

